"      Epivir (AE, AT, BE, BH, BR, CY, CZ, DE, DK, EE, EG, ES, FI, FR, GB, GR, HN, HR, IE, IL, IQ, IR, IT, JO, KW, LB, LU, LY, MT, NL, NO, OM, PE, PL, PT, PY, QA, RU, SA, SE, SG, SK, SY, TH, TR, VE, YE);",
